   help him in his last great work upon earth.<lb/>
   "Who am I", said he, "that God should send to<lb/>
   me a <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>*<notvariant>ssenger</notvariant></sic>
                     <corr>messenger</corr>
                  </choice> one among a thousand (meaning<lb/>
                  <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>t*t</sic>
                     <corr>that</corr>
                  </choice> Minister who had been praying<lb/>
   with<lb/>
   him <choice ana="illegible">
                     <sic>*<notvariant>ith</notvariant></sic>
                     <corr>with</corr>
